item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:

[quote=“Skiire, post:34, topic:440599”][quote author=Davidi2 link=topic=543278.msg3982321#msg3982321 date=1335440731]
More like I was implying you can’t bot straight on for that many hours (which your proggy proves), and yes also the fact that the profit/hr didn’t match up.
[/quote]

I’ve seen progress reports for a week+ straight. When I used my nexus fighter I would log two days+ straight. When I used RSBot (in that progress report) I would have to restart it though after a nights sleep or at school, etc.

In that particular progress report, no it doesn’t match up. Depending on the settings you can thieve more per hour and also which computer I was botting on affected profits.

inb4udidntmake16m I never said I stopped at the flat-rate 99.[/quote]

I did from 82~ through 99. Thank you for directly implying I’m a liar though, that’s a great way to promote your title.

178k/hr would mean it would have taken 90 hours of botting at that rate to bring me to the total of 16M. I can’t remember if I did anything extra, so at the worst case scenario I was in-fact wrong in my original post and it took me four days. I guess I am in-fact full of bullshit.
